OL,3,CCardiff City investigates alleged
OL,4,Cracist gesture in Lincoln City game
OL,6,FCardiff City FC has urged a fan
OL,7,Fsuspected of making a racist gesture
OL,8,Fat Saturday's game to turn themselves
OL,9,Fin.
OL,11,FThe fixture against Lincoln City FC
OL,12,Fwas stopped in the 55th minute after
OL,13,Fmatch officials were made aware of the
OL,14,Falleged abuse.
OL,16,FRob Street had put the visiting Imps
OL,17,Fahead before the incident which saw
OL,18,Freferee Tom Reeves approach both
OL,19,Fdugouts and speak to the managers.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/4
