OL,3,CCardiff City investigates alleged
OL,4,Cracist gesture in Lincoln City game
OL,6,FIt is believed the abuse was directed
OL,7,Ftowards Lincoln City's captain Tendayi
OL,8,FDarikwa.
OL,10,FIn a statement released today, Cardiff
OL,11,FCity said it was 'disgusted by this
OL,12,Frepugnant behaviour' and is working to
OL,13,Fidentify the individual sat in Ninian
OL,14,FStand Block 116 alongside South Wales
OL,15,FPolice.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/4
