OL,3,CCardiff City investigates alleged
OL,4,Cracist gesture in Lincoln City game
OL,6,FA club spokesperson said: "We ask
OL,7,Fsupporters to help with any
OL,8,Finformation pertaining to the
OL,9,Findividual's identity, or indeed for
OL,10,Fthe person to make themselves known to
OL,11,Fthe Club amidst an ongoing police
OL,12,Finvestigation.
OL,14,F"We are disgusted by this repugnant
OL,15,Fbehaviour and the impact it has had on
OL,16,Fthose affected."
OL,18,FMatch officials were also made aware
OL,19,Fof further anti-social behaviour when
OL,20,Fa vape was thrown at away team's
OL,21,Fgoalkeeper.
